    "originContent": "`codex-as-mcp` is a small **Model Context Protocol (MCP)** server that lets MCP clients (Claude Code, Cursor, etc.) delegate work to the **Codex CLI**.",
    "translatedContent": "`codex-as-mcp` es un pequeño servidor de **Model Context Protocol (MCP)** que permite a los clientes MCP (Claude Code, Cursor, etc.) delegar trabajo al **Codex CLI**."
