  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "TN8LYfy5dnUFy1lteGRwxgQJt4Ye4xwb7pNz8Pcvk08=",
    "originContent": "#### Example: third-party provider + `env_key`",
    "translatedContent": "#### Ejemplo: proveedor externo + `env_key`"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "6sFcoSyZbKWCuYQmc2FdXGDQtEfXA8gUv/c7SxseKu0=",
    "originContent": "If you're using a third-party provider, configure it in Codex `config.toml` and point `model_provider` at it. When a provider uses `env_key`, Codex CLI expects that env var to be present when it runs.",
    "translatedContent": "Si estás usando un proveedor externo, configúralo en el `config.toml` de Codex y apunta `model_provider` hacia él. Cuando un proveedor usa `env_key`, Codex CLI espera que esa variable de entorno esté presente cuando se ejecute."
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "hyiH5WPnWVf/wgsCEzJQTy3dCo85ZMuTBwhjv68Tza0=",
    "originContent": "Example:",
    "translatedContent": "Ejemplo:"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "E3uXOpXBPB3edL8+RLYBjnQiIHGkbC0yF2hcyGKXnwU=",
    "originContent": "```toml",
    "translatedContent": "```toml"
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "mR1ofFm5gckC09Ll49s/FhQ9RFlAJw6HvKInvgrvqq8=",
    "originContent": "model_provider = \"custom_provider\"",
    "translatedContent": "model_provider = \"custom_provider\""
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "GCF0lKPw4k0ggOZPrzLMTLIVVvXfyrv5AMkmGdQwa9c=",
    "originContent": "[model_providers.custom_provider]",
    "translatedContent": "[model_providers.custom_provider]"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "YNO9zzLf2ww0JQBmkP1NKWJQs3sUGC9zsoZiIv4Bh5o=",
    "originContent": "name = \"custom_provider\"",
    "translatedContent": "name = \"custom_provider\""
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "Fdu1y2BySANAbemGnhAvhrrRj5hpS9mtJJc2qFE5YXE=",
    "originContent": "base_url = \"https://...\"",
    "translatedContent": "base_url = \"https://...\""
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "O5tFEIYmD3TKOf5z8aCvBNLh6zjwp6qWWuNYT269oNk=",
    "originContent": "wire_api = \"responses\"",
    "translatedContent": "wire_api = \"responses\""
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "T1MIaK3u1tpZInnOtq3tbbrwpzbMzRDg24/DdcOlwCM=",
    "originContent": "env_key = \"PROVIDER_API_KEY\"",
    "translatedContent": "env_key = \"PROVIDER_API_KEY\""
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "oGAkZsAjpxou3TN/Q5D9KaR4ussAuSA2b0yLFSkOA8Q=",
    "originContent": "show_raw_agent_reasoning = true",
    "translatedContent": "show_raw_agent_reasoning = true"
